<br>
EQ is based loosely on the generic fantasy genre, with Lord of the Rings as the general basis for the genre.  Did you in LotR see:<br>
<br>
Gandalf: Ok, we're at a safe spot, Legolas, grab us some orcs, and make sure you don't aggro the Balrog in room 3.<br>
Legolas: ok.<br>
Legolas [to self]: last time I pull with no mezzers.  Can't believe Gandalf forgot an enchanter AGAIN!<br>
<br>
Instead, you saw the Fellowship move through the mines, checking every corner for traps and unknown dangers et.al.<br>
<br>
Someone, way back when, discovered how to FD pull, and off we went.  Fighting one mob at a time is more efficient you see, and it's all about efficiency. Can't be earning anything less than optimal experience at any time after all. <p><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=37379"><img src="http://www.velvetedge.org/sigs/kiztent.jpg"></a></center></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm17.showPrevMessage?topicID=182.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm17.showNextMessage?topicID=182.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm17.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=182.topic&index=16><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm17.emailToFriend?topicID=182.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm17.threadControl?topicID=182.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm17.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=182.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm17.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=182.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table b